    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for taking the time to share your comments and we were sorry to learn of your unsatisfactory experience with the pharmacy information you were given.  Pharmacy changes to their opening hours around the area are unfortunately out of our control, especially during these difficult and unprecedented times, however we appreciate your comments which we will forward to the team to make sure they advise patients to check opening times before they make the journey.

Should you remain dissatisfied and wish to discuss your experience further, please contact the Patient Advice and Liaison Service (PALS) at your earliest opportunity on telephone 0161 206 2003 or email pals@srft.nhs.uk quoting that you have been advised to do so via NHS Website, and they will do their best to address your concerns. 

